Package: ISPaL
Type: Package
Title: Periodic Forecasting with exogenous variables using PAR, PARX and RIDGE models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Thiago Lappicy; Carlos H. R. Lima
Maintainer: Thiago Lappicy <lappicy@gmail.com>
Description: This package was created for streamflow monthly forecasts with periodic
    models and climatic indicators, but the framework may be applied to various
    possibilities.
